<code>POST /v1/groups/{group_name}/features</code>
<h2>Create a New Feature Within a Group</h2>

<hr />

<pre>http://<%= request.host %>/api/v1/groups/{group_name}/features</pre>

<p>
  POSTing a request to this endpoint allows you to create a new feature within a group.  Upon success,
  it will return a representation of the feature you have just created.
</p>

<%
  groups      = feature_service.get_groups
  first_group = groups.first || "pubserv"
%>

<h4>Example Request</h4>

<p>The following curl request would add a new feature to the group &quot;<%= first_group %>&quot;:</p>

<pre>
curl -X POST -d 'feature[name]=show-new-feature&feature[description]=Show+new+feature%3F&feature[enabled]=false' \
  http://<%= request.host %>/api/v1/groups/<%= first_group %>/features
</pre>

<h4>Example Response</h4>

<pre>
{
    "feature": {
        "description": "Show new feature?",
        "enabled": false,
        "group": "pubserv",
        "name": "show-new-feature"
    }
}
</pre>

